name: Bob Harper
bio: He/Him/His All things health and wellness. Photographer and dad to Karl,Vivienne & Ralph.  @bobharpergallery is my other page.

social_posts.post_text: Look Who showed up at my doorstep last night. @rezafarahan and I go WAY BACK as you can see from the second pic. Here’s to a friendship of over 30 years and going strong. I love you, mook.
Christmas ain’t ready for me 🎅🏻
MERRY CHRISTMAS. SENDING OUT ALL THE LOVE TODAY 🎄 🤶🎅🏻🧑‍🎄
It’s a Christmas tradition to watch A Christmas Story every year. What’s your tradition?
Baby, it’s cold outside.
Vivienne Westwood was an ICON and a BAD ASS QUEEN. One of my dog’s has her name. That’s how much I loved her. RIP. The fashion in Heaven is gonna be ON FIRE 🖤🖤🖤
January’s…am I right?
This is NOT A PAID ENDORSEMENT!! My good friend @rachaelray makes this 24/7 seasoning and I gotta tell you, it has made my simple January eating an absolute TREAT!!! I love you Rachael!!
Pray for KARL today. I am stressed out!!!
Karl got 9 teeth extracted! My poor boy.
Thanks for ALL THE LOVE TODAY
Serving Thom Browne today for a show talking about game shows. My all time favorite is Paul Lynde, center square on Hollywood Squares AND Survivor. What’s your favorite game show?
KING KARL is back and I couldn’t be happier!!!
90min with @iamicaniwillido on my @onepeloton with my @hotsuit.global CRAZY!!!!!
Have you seen MEGAN yet!? It was so much fun!!
Thanks to @cpkimball for such a great Ginger Scallion steamed fish recipe. It was a big hit at dinner last night!!
Wanna know how cold it is in Soho… ask Karl.
Yeah, it’s F’ING COLD!!!
Best way to spend Valentine’s Day was being at the @thombrowne fashion show. It was OUT OF THIS WORLD!!!
Still in a @thombrowne dream.
Life in Soho with my dogs on a rainy day.
Icing my knee with my nurse at my feet. Vivienne is the best!
Not letting a torn meniscus stop my fashion. We forge ahead…no matter what. Surgery in April. Stay tuned. 🖤🖤🖤
Leaning into ALL JAPANESE DENIM and my brace. 🤷‍♂️
See…I don’t just wear black 🖤🖤🖤
Friday is all about John Wick Chapter 4. Who else is excited about this movie!!!?!
Dressed for @johnwickmovie tonight. Would you expect anything less from me!? 🖤🖤🖤
The sun is out in NYC. I definitely needed it, am I right?? 🖤🖤🖤
Monday’s got me BLUE.
Sun’s out…GUNS OUT 🖤🖤🖤
On a rainy Wednesday you might as well bring out TAILS 🖤🖤🖤
Knee surgery today went well. This we me before i went into the operating room. I just got home and I’m out of it. I’ll be keeping you posted on my recovery. Thanks for all the love 🖤🖤🖤

Day One of my knee surgery. I tore my medial meniscus, thank you @iamicaniwillido  I slept like a rock last night and I have my dogs helping me along with @briantatara being the best nurse. Ever. Thanks for all the love 🖤🖤🖤
This is the night that took me to knee surgery. I blame @agnesofficial for the BEST SONG and @iamicaniwillido for getting the DJ to play it twice!!! I still say it was worth it! 😂
Day 2. Knee pain ain’t great but I really wanted to go outside for a minute and feel the sun on my face. Don’t judge my outfit. I just got out of bed. 😆
I was a bit too ambitious going out to get a shave @thebarbernewyorkofficial I’m going home now and get flat on my back. The pain ain’t fun today. Photo by @briantatara
Day 5 of recovery. Doing good. Just can’t walk, AT ALL!!! I’ve watched two great shows!! BEEF and SWARM. Have y’all seen them yet!!?
Getting my stitches out today. My doctor is really happy with how my knee is looking. Also great news for my boys @smithstreettattooparlour He stayed away from my STAY GOLD tattoo. More good news!!

Okay so it’s been 7 days since my surgery and things are progressing nicely. I managed to take my dogs out this morning, by myself!! It was a bit ambitious but it went well and of course I picked up their poop. 😂 Gonna ICE now.
Trying out one crutch just around the house. I started PT yesterday and it went well. He has me relearning how to walk and put about 30% of my weight on the knee. Slow and steady wins the race!
Day 12 of recovery. Took the dogs out for a walk with one crutch. It’s definitely an adjustment. So glad to be out on this glorious day!
NEWS ALERT! I am gonna try to teach my hot yoga class next Friday at 3:30pm @bodenyc Flatiron. I WILL BE ON MY CRUTCHES!! Working on the playlist now!! SIGN UP NOW!
Are you drinking enough water?
Thursday, almost 3 weeks since my knee surgery. PT and being smart and most of all, PATIENCE 🖤🖤🖤
No way I was missing the wrap party for my dear friend @rachaelray @rachaelrayshow last night. She is a true ICON. There was so much love here tonight and @johnmcusimano and his band were ON FIRE!!
It feels like SUMMER!!!

Well I went to the gym yesterday for the first time since surgery. I just did upper body and core. Let me tell you, I woke up SORE!!!! I was a little self conscious being on crutches but did it anyway. Who cares, right!?
Physical Therapy is a GODSEND!
Let’s do this!
Walking around in my apartment without crutches. It’s a BIG DAY!!!
It’s Tuesday. Gonna try out my cane. Just as long as there are NO STAIRS!!!
Are my legs gonna get any sun today. 😂
Wednesday night @apparatusstudio with my girl @_taracarroll Gorgeous night 🖤🖤🖤
Taylor Swift fans are CRAZY!!! 75 thousand people singing every word of EVERY SONG at the top of their lungs. I’ve never seen anything like it. 😜our seats were INSANE!
I Guess Im a SWIFTIE. Yeah, I got a t-shirt. 😛
Hello, Los Angeles!! Home away from home.

Today the love of my life is graduating high school. It was like yesterday when Coco was just a little girl and now she’s a woman. I’m so proud of you and love you so much. Onward to UT Austin HOOK ‘EM
Oh Canada. Outside my apartment windows right now. It’s out of Bladerunner!! NO FILTER
I went to get my haircut… I guess he wanted to chop ALL MY HAIR OFF!! 🤷‍♂️
Pride in Nyack at this great little wine and cheese place. Queer owned.
PROUD QUEER… EVERYDAY. #nyackpride
Vivienne is living her best life helping Benjamin at work yesterday @thombrowne SHE FITS RIGHT IN. Move over, Hector.
Why so BLUE. Wednesday night vibes.
Can I get an AMEN

Earlier this week, I sat down with #CheddarNews to talk about my heart attack recovery journey and the importance of having community support through #SurvivorsHaveHeart – especially during the tough times. 
 
Check out the link in my story or visit SurvivorsHaveHeart.com for more information. #sponsored
HAPPY PRIDE 🏳️‍🌈 Spread LOVE today and EVERYDAY. I love y’all 🖤🖤🖤
Saturday. Before yoga. Ready for the sweat.
Okay I am OBSESSED with @bakedbymelissa green goddess salad dressing. I put it on cabbage, cucumber and chives. Melissa ain’t messing around! I’m gonna have to try that @lenwich hummus sandwich next!
Friday night. I drink tequila and listen to country music.

Matt’s power zone endurance is the REAL DEAL. He is a great Coach and keeps you focused on goals and talks about health and fitness. He ain’t trying to be anything other than that and I’m hear for it.
When Thom&Rick collide…I’m here for it.
Tuesday night in Soho. Beat the heat with a lewk.
This is me doing casual. Can you believe Karl is 15 years old!! He’s my best friend.

@bobharper 
Whole outfit: @thombrowne
I love a Trainer, Coach or Group Fitness Instructor that doesn’t feel like they have to fill the space with just a bunch of words. Choose your words carefully and thoughtfully.
I love Karl… SO F’ING MUCH.

Those of you that know me KNOW that I love this man. His name is TYLER CHILDERS. Do yourself a favor and watch is new video IN YOUR LOVE. It dissolved me into tears. I can’t wait to see his concert with @_taracarroll here in NYC on August 2. I F’ing love you, TYLER!
This message is a thank you to @timmytychilders I LOVE YOU
This photo says it all. The coolest person I know. Love of my life. #rideordie
One of my stories about being bullied growing up. A big shout out and thank you all y’all giving me love and support. Big love to Tyler Childers for just being so COOL.

I am experiencing the most intense heartbreak that I have ever felt. My sweet dog and best friend KARL left this earth on Friday. This first photo was taken the day before he died. He was 16 years old and I loved him so much. If you ever had the chance to meet him you will know exactly what Im saying. There is one photo here when I was in the hospital after my heart attack. He always just wanted to be by my side. I rescued him but let me tell you, he was the one doing the rescuing. Rest in peace my sweet boy. I miss you so much…💔
This photo tells you exactly how much JOY Karl brought to my life. R.I.P. my sweet baby boy.
Birthday suit.
Vivienne was the best date last night @onewhitestreet If you don’t know about this restaurant…now you do. Special. Effortless and the food was divine.
Figuring out what life is like without Karl. I posted a photo of Vivienne on @bobharpergallery  going through the same emotions. Thanks @nellcan for capturing this. I love you.
Had a great time last night on this ship…or is it a boat!? The name felt appropriate.

My last night in Amsterdam I met this little angel in one of the coolest places in Amsterdam. Great vibe. Amazing wine and food and to the group of people that I met, thanks you for being so kind. You were such good medicine.
Vivienne and I have become even more attached if that is possible.
Spending the day with my girl.

I had such a wonderful time with my friends from @astrazeneca in Amsterdam last week. It’s always so special for me to meet other heart attack survivors, share our stories, and help lift each other up ❤️
 
I’m proud to be a part of #SurvivorsHaveHeart now and always! #sponsored
On the train going Upstate today. Vivienne is always by my side these days. Best friends.
Do you just ever feel like a cocktail at 3pm on a Tuesday?
Original staircase in one of the Rockefeller mansions in NYC.
People keep telling me I should start doing a GRWM. I’m open to your thoughts on the matter.
Feel like I haven’t worn all black in a minute which is crazy because I used to only wear black. Thanks @thombrowne 🖤🖤🖤

Since the passing of my sweet Karl, Vivienne and I have been inseparable. We go almost everywhere together. It might be time to bring in a new family member. For both of us. A big thank you to my friends @thebarbernewyorkofficial and @mitsuru_groomer for always welcoming my baby girl.
I guess I’m in my PREP SCHOOL ERA today.

Since losing my 16 year old dog Karl two months ago, it has been a devastating loss for me. This little puppy was brought to my attention and I acted on it immediately. Everyone welcome Ralph Lauren Harper. Im a member of the dachshund world and I’m hear for it!
This is the look of pure love. Say hello to Ralph. He is definitely helping to mend the broken hearts that Vivienne and I have had since Karl’s passing.
Vivienne ain’t having Ralph right now. Any tips???!!
Vivienne is working out some issues.
Ralph absolutely cannot stand the rain and it has been rainy for 4 days. SOS!!!
First day out with RALPH with no rain. You don’t realize how loud NYC is until you have a tiny puppy. He refuses to go potty. He will get used to the sounds, right!!???
Ralph inspired my color palette today. Look at his face!!! Quick update, the loud noises of the City are really scaring this baby. He will get used to it, right!?
null
Friday night is gonna be CRAZY!!! #bestnightever
Saturday Night Fever. Vesper martinis and Manhattans. 🖤🖤🖤
The Harper Family out on a gorgeous day in the City. Now let’s just pray that Ralph eventually pees on the streets outside. He won’t!!!
Ralph is slowly getting the vibe of NYC.
Ralph is ready for the week. He’s getting more confident out on the streets. Potty training is moving along. It’s all about patience. He LOVES FETCH!!
We went to visit Aunt Tara yesterday @apparatusstudio Ralph felt right at home that that beautiful gallery.
Vivienne is slowly TOLERATING Ralph which is a step in the right direction. Lots of treats are involved.
Ralph has really taken to Karl’s old bed. It breaks my heart and makes me happy at the same time.
Wednesday look. I wonder why people always ask me if I work at Thom Browne. Haha 🤷‍♂️
Ralph finding his light and his new life in Soho.
Sunday morning 🖤🖤🖤
I’m making sure that Vivienne knows that she is MY QUEEN.
Mondays… am I right
I think I might be ready for a puppy training session. Any takers!? Haha
The Harper’s were out having a coffee and this photo was taken in our neighborhood. I love this photo. Thank you @susieloveart 🖤🖤🖤
Thursday night ain’t ready.
Just my regular Sunday morning 🤷‍♂️
Last night’s dinner celebrating Thom Browne’s 20 year anniversary in the fashion world was nothing short of POSH, GLAMOUR and ICONIC. I was in Heaven and it was all shades of grey

Last night the first comment Thom Browne said to me was “why aren’t you wearing a skirt” I DIED!  If he only knew that I am MOSTLY in his skirts!! Today The Harpers are walking the streets. Vivienne just got the cutest haircut and Ralph is killing his Thom Browne sweater.
Well I guess the dogs need their sweaters today.
Ralph is dressed up and ready for the day. Look at this adorable bow tie!!!
Congratulations @thombrowne for TWENTY YEARS ❤️🤍💙 FASHION ICON
OMG!!!! Vivienne just got her teeth cleaned from @doggy_dental and Anya did a GREAT JOB!!!! It was fast and when you see the before and after you’ll see how great they look!!!

Last night @lee_minjin house was sublime. Some of the best food I’ve ever eaten in a house filled with nothing but LOVE. I’m still full!! Oh yeah and I got to meet Lucy Liu aka O-Ren Ishii. Best night ever!!
These two song will definitely be on my playlist today @bodenyc 3:30pm Flatiron. Are you comin’ 🖤🖤🖤
It’s Friday and Ralph is sunbathing.
Thanks @mattwilpers @onepeloton for the beat down yesterday. 2 hour ride. There was a lot of mental strength for this workout. Has anyone else done this!?!?
Happy Thanksgiving, y’all!!
Thanksgiving was serving tonight.
Ralph is feeling it
What do you think Ralph is thinking about in this photo?
This is what Wednesday looks like with my girl Tara. We are serving GOTH PROM PICTURE.  Starting the birthday celebrations @rwguild
Friday morning. Ready for the weekend.
On my roof with the dogs.

The Queen has arrived in NYC and I couldn’t be happier! We started with drinks last night at @lamercerieny @rwguild Carl can make the best cocktails and Ryan is THE MAN! I love this woman with all of my heart.
The Princess Coco is in the building. Life is good. My baby girl.
I can’t get this song outta my head @nickiminaj
Because why WOULDNT I have a Thom Browne Christmas tree. ❤️ 🤍 💙
It’s beginning to look a lot like Christmas.
Merry Christmas from The Harpers in Soho. 🎄❤️🎄
My new favorite spot in my neighborhood. Books, coffee and wine. What more do you need.
Happy New Year, Y’ALL 🖤🖤🖤
Ralph is growing up and he is an angel.
Snow on my beanie. Wine in my glass. Thanks @bibliothequenyc
Sweater Weather for Ralph 🥶
